9217363850145890", "url": "https://x.com/printtie_offcl/status/2069217363850145890", "text": "티티가 추천하는 오늘의 프린티! #OOTT🦊🐺\n\n'뿌너' 작가님의 작품을 감상해보세요!\n🥳작가님의 생일을 축하드립니다🎉\n울보 도율🖤엉아 재현이와 함께 \n행복한 하루 되시길 바라요🥹\n#더_리쉬드 #The_Leashed #율재 #도율재현 \n\n@bboom_oct \nhttps://t.co/Ze152xAxJ2", "time": "00:33", "author": "printtie_offcl", "author_name": "프린티 공식", "followers": 2022, "views": 5348, "likes": 28, "replies": 0, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": false, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": []}}, {"id": "2069291045351727610", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2069291045351727610", "text": "US SPR crude inventories in million barrels - sour vs sweet (DOE) #oott https://t.co/A15RwdLHnx", "time": "05:26", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6822, "likes": 45, "replies": 1, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2069307297159901673", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2069307297159901673", "text": "If you are counting Strait of Hormuz barrels, don’t forget to add the bypass pipelines if you want an apples-to-apples comparison to pre-war levels. \n\nWhat matters is not SoH flows, but Persian Gulf flows. As long as the bypass pipelines continue to be used (and they are), SoH volumes don’t need to ", "time": "06:31", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 81785, "likes": 754, "replies": 41, "retweets": 112, "quotes": 13, "bookmarks": 69, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2069339952312369262", "url": "https://x.com/diepthaolong/status/2069339952312369262", "text": "And yes, I bought some more #oil long positions at $72.8 today.\nRisky. But my indicators giving long signals, so… ☕️\n\n#oott #WTI", "time": "08:41", "author": "diepthaolong", "author_name": "Viv", "followers": 443, "views": 9898, "likes": 119, "replies": 10, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2069359278964535683", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2069359278964535683", "text": "Iran says the Strait of Hormuz is “fully” open to commercial shipping and that large volumes of oil have been transported through the waterway in recent days, according to the semi-official Iranian Students’ News Agency.", "time": "09:57", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 51628, "likes": 357, "replies": 27, "retweets": 71, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2069408176579989518", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2069408176579989518", "text": "Iran-Oman joint statement on the future of the Strait of Hormuz. Note the wording about “services” and “costs” https://t.co/9ml4ulx9eV", "time": "13:12", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 105246, "likes": 564, "replies": 40, "retweets": 226, "quotes": 40, "bookmarks": 117, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2069432177432178817", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2069432177432178817", "text": "The oil market feels more and more like the movie The Big Short.\n\nYou can see what's coming, but the market is going the other way #OOTT https://t.co/pyH9IrEl3D", "time": "14:47", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 51513, "likes": 167, "replies": 13, "retweets": 16, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2069452458141618684", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2069452458141618684", "text": "US Sec. Of State Rubio: No Country Is Allowed To Charge Tolls Or Fees On An Int’l Waterway, That Is Existing Int’l Law\n\n#OOTT", "time": "16:08", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 21339, "likes": 12, "replies": 3, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2069457030717350042", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2069457030717350042", "text": "On the Strait of Hormuz, note that the U.S. says no “tolls” allowed; Iran and Oman however are discussing “costs” for “services” provided.", "time": "16:26", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 40296, "likes": 245, "replies": 27, "retweets": 44, "quotes": 7, "bookmarks": 14, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2069459433206259846", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2069459433206259846", "text": "@dantannNYC As long as Chinese banks (and a few others in Asia) do, Iran is fine. Let’s see if Indian, Japanese, South Korean and others reject dealing with Iran; my guess is that if it’s legal, they will engage (see Japan buying Russian crude, for example)", "time": "16:35", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 11731, "likes": 23, "replies": 2, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "China demand"]}}, {"id": "2069482976170103238", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2069482976170103238", "text": "Hormuz Transits Rebound to 4.8 Mbd as Stranded Tonnage and Sanctioned Fleets Clear Blockade #OOTT", "time": "18:09", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 21304, "likes": 96, "replies": 5, "retweets": 19, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2069498009210220948", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2069498009210220948", "text": "Rabobank's oil call is simple: \n\nThe Hormuz risk premium is fading faster than the physical disruption.\n\nBrent falls from ~$79 this year to ~$72 by 2028.\n\nReasonable near-term. \n\nMuch harder to believe over the long term.\n\n#Oil #Brent #OOTT #Energy #Commodities #Markets @pumpingoilniron", "time": "19:09", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 6202, "likes": 38, "replies": 6, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2069515439961477170", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2069515439961477170", "text": "“… enabled China to slash crude oil imports by 40% – or 4.6 million barrels per day – between February and May, helping significantly to ease wider pressures in the global market…”\n\nhttps://t.co/Afdbmcr9rK", "time": "20:18", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 30058, "likes": 118, "replies": 3, "retweets": 29, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 37, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["China demand", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2069519539478368457", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2069519539478368457", "text": "The @IEA reckons that UAE reached ~85% of pre-war oil exports in early June (ie, before the MoU was signed) thanks to a combination of bypass pipeline, Fujairah strategic storage and, importantly, dark SoH crossing along the Omani coastline. \n\nIn early June, IEA puts UAE total oil exports (crude and", "time": "20:34", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 109026, "likes": 374, "replies": 28, "retweets": 101, "quotes": 11, "bookmarks": 87, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2069520457041056153", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2069520457041056153", "text": "BUCKLE UP! \nAPI Inventory Moves 06/23\n\nCrude -765,000\nGasoline +1.238 million \nDistillates +1.447 million \nCushing -982,000 (estimated level around 19.1 million)\n\nSPR -9.1 million (lowest level in more than 40 years)\n\n#oott #crudeoil #gasoline #api", "time": "20:38", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 94799, "likes": 399, "replies": 28, "retweets": 71, "quotes": 13, "bookmarks": 22, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 28, "views": 140514, "likes": 327}, {"username": "JavierBlas", "name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "tweets": 9, "views": 444283, "likes": 2448}, {"username": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "tweets": 7, "views": 20459, "likes": 108}, {"username": "LiveSquawk", "name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "tweets": 3, "views": 56047, "likes": 32}, {"username": "avionsunantiqu1", "name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "tweets": 3, "views": 59340, "likes": 300}], "top_authors_by_views": [{"username": "JavierBlas", "name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "tweets": 9, "views": 444283, "likes": 2448}, {"username": "staunovo", "nam